### Onboarding Module HTTP Tests
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/onboarding
@onboardingId = 693a80057e07119e5fd6a8df
@employeeId = 693a80047e07119e5fd6a8d9
@contractId = 693a80047e07119e5fd6a8d3
@taskName = Complete I-9 Form

# ==========================================
# 1. Onboarding Initialization & Checklists (ONB-001)
# ==========================================

### Candidate Upload Contract & Forms
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload-contract
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ownerId": "{{employeeId}}",
    "type": "Contract",
    "url": "http://example.com/signed_contract.pdf"
}

### Create Onboarding Checklist
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "contractId": "{{contractId}}",
    "employeeId": "{{employeeId}}",
    "department": "Engineering"
}

### Get All Onboarding Checklists
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get Onboarding by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{onboardingId}}

### Add Task to Checklist
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{onboardingId}}/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Setup Dev Environment",
    "department": "Engineering",
    "deadline": "2026-02-05",
    "description": "Install request software stack."
}

# ==========================================
# 2. Tracking & Employee View (ONB-004, ONB-005)
# ==========================================

### Get Contract Details (ONB-002)
GET {{baseUrl}}/contracts/{{contractId}}

### Get Onboarding by Employee ID (Tracker)
GET {{baseUrl}}/employee/{{employeeId}}

### Get Onboarding Progress
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{onboardingId}}/progress

### Update Task Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/{{onboardingId}}/tasks/{{taskName}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "completed"
}

### Get Pending Tasks (Reminders)
GET {{baseUrl}}/employee/{{employeeId}}/pending-tasks

# ==========================================
# 3. Documents (ONB-007)
# ==========================================

### Upload Compliance Document
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ownerId": "{{employeeId}}",
    "type": "ID_Card",
    "url": "http://example.com/id_card.jpg",
    "expiryDate": "2030-01-01"
}

### Get Documents by Owner
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/owner/{{employeeId}}

### Link Document to Task
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/{{onboardingId}}/tasks/{{taskName}}/document
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "documentId": "DOC_ID_PLACEHOLDER"
}

# ==========================================
# 4. Operations & Provisioning (ONB-009, ONB-012, ONB-013)
# ==========================================

### Provision System Access
POST {{baseUrl}}/provision-access
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "employeeId": "{{employeeId}}",
    "systems": ["Email", "Jira", "GitHub", "Slack"]
}

### Reserve Equipment
POST {{baseUrl}}/reserve-equipment
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "employeeId": "{{employeeId}}",
    "items": ["MacBook Pro", "Monitor", "Keyboard"]
}

### Schedule Access Revocation
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedule-access-revocation
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "employeeId": "{{employeeId}}",
    "revocationDate": "2027-01-01"
}

# ==========================================
# 5. Payroll & Finalization (ONB-018, ONB-019, ONB-020)
# ==========================================

### Trigger Payroll Initiation
POST {{baseUrl}}/trigger-payroll-initiation
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "contractId": "{{contractId}}"
}

### Process Signing Bonus
POST {{baseUrl}}/contracts/{{contractId}}/process-signing-bonus

### Cancel Onboarding (No-Show)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{onboardingId}}/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "reason": "Candidate did not show up on first day."
}